EnrolStudent.description:
Create an Enrolment for a student. PLease note that End Date is an JSON array. The full example is like this:
 {intake_date:false, programme_length:false, custom_date:'2021-05-25'}
 The first option that is set to "true" will be used, if no option is set to "true" custom date will be used.

